text: Jason David Frank (September 4, 1973 – November 19, 2022) was an American actor and martial artist. He was best known for his role as Tommy Oliver in the Power Rangers franchise. He committed suicide on November 19, 2022. ==Filmography== ===Television=== * Mighty Morphin Power Rangers – Tommy Oliver / Green Ranger / White Ranger (1993–1996) * Mighty Morphin Alien Rangers – Tommy Oliver (1996) * Power Rangers Zeo – Tommy Oliver / Red Zeo Ranger (1996) * Power Rangers Turbo – Tommy Oliver / Red Turbo Ranger (1997) * Power Rangers Wild Force – Tommy Oliver / Red Zeo Ranger (2002) * Power Rangers Dino Thunder – Dr. Tommy Oliver / Black Dino Ranger (2004) * Power Rangers Megaforce – Dr. Tommy Oliver / Green Ranger / White Ranger (2014) * Power Rangers Ninja Steel – Dr. Tommy Oliver / Green Ranger / White Ranger / Red Zeo Ranger / Black Dino Ranger / Robot Tommy (2018) ===Movies=== * Mighty Morphin Power Rangers: The Movie – Tommy Oliver / White Ranger (1995) * Turbo: A Power Rangers Movie – Tommy Oliver / Red Turbo Ranger (1997) * Power Rangers – Angel Grove Citizen (2017) * Mighty Morphin Power Rangers: Once & Always – Tommy Oliver / Green Ranger Voice (2023) ==Other websites== * Category:1973 births Category:2022 deaths Category:American martial artists Category:American movie actors Category:American television actors
